===Etymology===

{{Distinguish2|[[Romanians|Romanians]], unrelated ethnic group}}

From {{etyl|rom|en}} {{term|rom||man|lang=rom}}, probably ultimately from {{etyl|sa|en}} {{term|tr=doma|डोम||member of a low caste of travelling musicians and dancers|lang=sa}}. See some more information at '''''[[Roma]]'''''.

The other major categories of words for the Roma are cognates of ''[[Gypsy]]'' (words related to ''[[Egypt]]'') and cognates of ''[[tzigane]]'' (words derived from Greek); see those entries for more information.

